    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half, then peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1694421962545-x200.jpg",
