            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until starting to break up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694421965796-x200.jpg",
