            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>free range chicken</strong> <strong>breast portion[s] </strong>into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
