            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, increase the heat to medium-high, then add the <strong>chicken pieces</strong> to the pan with the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and cook for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>warming</strong> <strong>free range chicken bhuna</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
